modName: Chaos's Guide to Swift Steeds Stables v3.1
summary: A guide for finding the bonus horses of FieryMarigold's Swift Steeds Stables mod v3.1
descriptionHtml:
A guide for finding the bonus horses of FieryMarigold's Swift Steeds Stables mod v3.1. The guide is a .docx file, so I wouldn't recommend downloading it through NMM, unless you want it to install the .docx file inside your Skyrim/Data/ folder. Some of the images posted here are in the guide, but there are also some bonus images posted here that aren't in the guide. Refer to these if needed.

FieryMarigold's mod can be found here:


http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/49727/?tab=2&navtag=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nexusmods.com%2Fskyrim%2Fajax%2Fmodfiles%2F%3Fid%3D49727&pUp=1
author: Chaos aka kichigaikikyokagome
